content:
Different colors painted on masks
represent different personalities, but
when you paint a flowery face, things get tricky!{做鬼脸}

There's a rumor in the Metropolis,
if you keep walking along the Station, keep walking,
you'll find yourself back at Central Station.

But then people complained it was too spicy,
so they added strawberries to the tofu soup, {什么？}
That's culinary heresy!
